Currently, webdar is still a work in progress,

you can compile it my issuing 'make' in the
src subdirectory:

    cd src
    make

you will get a webdar binary ready to be run

   see the man page for the few switchs you
   will need,

   cd ../man
   man ./webdar.1

when webdar will be close to be at release 1.0.0
autoconf, and automake will be used to provide
portability and installation process of binary
man page and documentation, patience...
